    <item>
      <title>太平洋投资管理公司 (Pimco) 总裁 Wilding 称美联储仍有降息空间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-04/there-s-still-room-for-the-fed-to-cut-pimco-s-wilding-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Pimco 经济学家蒂芙尼·怀尔丁 (Tiffany Wilding) 对 9 月份美国就业报告作出了回应。怀尔丁在“彭博未平仓合约”上表示，美国经济正在放缓，但并未崩溃，而且看起来更加“正常”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-04/there-s-still-room-for-the-fed-to-cut-pimco-s-wilding-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 19:32:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芝加哥学校董事会所有成员因预算混乱而辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/all-chicago-school-board-members-to-resign-amid-budget-chaos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥教育委员会的所有七名成员将于本月晚些时候辞职，这将结束该市与其学区之间数月来不断升级的紧张关系，因为双方都面临着巨大的赤字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/all-chicago-school-board-members-to-resign-amid-budget-chaos</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 18:30:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Oaktree 支持的 STG 削减债务协议，颠覆债权人评级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/oaktree-backed-stg-cuts-debt-deal-that-upends-creditor-ranks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，私募股权支持的 STG Logistics 与一群贷款机构达成协议，彻底改革其债务结构，并使其在还款优先权方面领先于同行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/oaktree-backed-stg-cuts-debt-deal-that-upends-creditor-ranks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 17:52:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元创两年来最佳一周表现 其它货币大幅下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/dollar-set-for-best-week-in-two-years-as-big-fed-cut-bets-erased</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美元正经历 2022 年以来最好的一周。地缘政治动荡、海外借贷成本降低的可能性以及美国经济的韧性，都在刺激世界储备货币走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/dollar-set-for-best-week-in-two-years-as-big-fed-cut-bets-erased</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 16:02:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业数据对债券市场造成冲击，交易员撤出对美联储大幅降息的押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/traders-wipe-out-bets-on-big-fed-cuts-as-jobs-data-hits-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国九月份就业数据超出预期并预示着强劲的招聘趋势后，交易员大幅削减了对美联储未来降息步伐的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/traders-wipe-out-bets-on-big-fed-cuts-as-jobs-data-hits-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 12:49:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市收盘接近盘中高点；收益率攀升：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就业报告强于预期，迫使交易员重新考虑美联储下次降息幅度，美国国债下跌。由于数据凸显了美国经济的韧性并提振了软着陆的希望，股市收盘接近盘中高点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 22:27:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
